{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>If you're looking for a challenge, you've found it!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Easy Ball Game is a brand new game that unlike its name is an extremely difficult game based on the Only UP style of play!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Climbing has you rolling, jumping and testing your balance. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The game consists of several zones with different graphic styles and obstacles all to be discovered. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/Video_senza_titolo_-_Realizzato_con_Clipchamp.gif?t=1734873239\" /></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You can change skins to your ball and unlock new ones! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>For the first time in the genre there are also NPCs, which interact with you and give you funny tips and comments!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/Video_senza_titolo_-_Realizzato_con_Clipchamp__2_.gif?t=1734873239\" /></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The ball control system is completely physics-based.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>If you are looking for an intriguing, rabid and psychological challenge, Easy Ball Game is for you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Easy Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>learn the path without too obvious dangers, because thanks to some life-saving mats, you won't risk falling all the way down! Plus, you'll unlock an exclusive skin by completing it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/image2.png?t=1734873239\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Impossible Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In impossible mode there will be no checkpoints and teleports! It was created for those who love the challenge.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/image.png?t=1734873239\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Quest Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Quest mode offers new paths that will come with new updates and will offer new challenges!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/quest.png?t=1734873239\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Change Skin</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In every modes, you can find this funny cylinder which once in, you will be able to change your current skin and unlocked skins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Teleport Zone (Checkpoints)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This little guy here can be found in the normal mode and in the easy mode. This is basically a teleport machine which teleports you on the last checkpoint saved. Checkpoints will be saved every surpassed Zone, so like: ZONE 1- ZONE 2- ZONE 3- ZONE 4.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Hallowen Special - Free DLC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture down the new Hallowen-themed path, filled with frightening dangers, obstacles and waterfalls of blood. Unlock exclusive skins such as the eye and super pumpkin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151020/extras/photo_5819211736237065235_y.jpg?t=1734873239\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ju